France advance from Group C into the knockout stages, Peru advance to the airport to fly back home. Peru will be out of the World Cup if they fail to avoid defeat. A France win would ensure they join Russia and Uruguay in the last-16 of the competition. Team News – France Lloris, Pavard, Varane, Umtiti, Lucas, Pogba, Kante, Mbappe, Griezmann, Matuidi, Giroud.
Subs: Mandanda, Kimpembe, Lemar, Dembele, Tolisso, Nzonzi, Rami, Fekir, Sidibe, Thauvin, Mendy, Areola. Team News – Peru Gallese, Advincula, Ramos, Rodriguez, Trauco, Aquino, Yotun, Carrillo, Cueva, Flores, Guerrero.
Subs: Caceda, Corzo, Santamaria, Araujo, Hurtado, Farfan, Ruidiaz, Tapia, Polo, Cartagena, Loyola, Carvallo. Referee: Mohammed Abdulla Hassan (United Arab Emirates)